# Project Overview

This is an ABC Admin application with a monorepo structure using NX for workspace management. The application consists of:

## Architecture
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root package configuration
- [nx.json](mdc:nx.json) - NX workspace configuration

## Frontend (Next.js)
- [apps/web/src/app](mdc:apps/web/src/app) - Next.js app router
- [apps/web/src/components](mdc:apps/web/src/components) - Reusable UI components
- [apps/web/src/contexts](mdc:apps/web/src/contexts) - React context providers
- [apps/web/src/hooks](mdc:apps/web/src/hooks) - Custom React hooks
- [apps/web/src/utils](mdc:apps/web/src/utils) - Utility functions
- [apps/web/tailwind.config.js](mdc:apps/web/tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration

## Backend (NestJS)
- [apps/api/src/main.ts](mdc:apps/api/src/main.ts) - API entry point
- [apps/api/src/app](mdc:apps/api/src/app) - NestJS application modules
- [apps/api/src/db](mdc:apps/api/src/db) - Database related files
- [apps/api/typeorm.config.ts](mdc:apps/api/typeorm.config.ts) - TypeORM configuration

## Shared Libraries
- [libs](mdc:libs) - Shared libraries and utilities
